node.title: Cleo Smith found alive by WA police
node.alt: Cleo Smith smiles for a photo while holding up paper Easter eggs on sticks outside.
node.description: WA police say missing four-year-old girl Cleo Smith has been found safe and well in a locked house in Carnarvon.
node.content: ["Missing four-year-old girl Cleo Smith has been found safe and well in a locked house in Carnarvon, WA police say.", "According to a statement, police broke into the house about 1am and found her in one of the rooms.", "One of the officers picked her up and asked her, 'What's your name?\"", "She replied: \"My name is Cleo.\"", "She has been reunited with her parents.", "WA police said a Carnarvon man had been taken into custody and was being questioned by detectives.", "Cleo\u00a0had been missing since October 16, having disappeared from the tent she was sleeping in with her parents\u00a0at at the Blowholes, a popular camping site north of Carnarvon.", "Her disappearance sparked a widespread search across the whole of Western Australia.", "More to come."]
